{"word":"τριχίασις","slug":"τριχίασις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n105406\" key=\"trixi/asis\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">τρῐχ-ίᾱσις</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">εως</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <sense id=\"n105406.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a disease of the eyelids, when they are introverted, and the lashes irritate the eye</tr_> (opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐκτρόπιον</foreign>), <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.437</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Sever.</author> </bibl> ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0718.tlg007:68\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aët.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.68</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n105406.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a disease of the urethra, when the urine is full of small hair-like substances,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17(2).768</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n105406.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a disease in the breasls of women giving suck, such that the nipples crack into fine fissures,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Erot.</author> </bibl> </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n105406.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a fissure, scratch</tr_> in a bone, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Pall.</author> </bibl> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in Hp.Fract.</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2123.tlg001:12:273\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.273</biblScope> </bibl> C., [<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> </bibl>]<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.782</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}